NLquery: How many base models are there in total?
List all internet service providers and their endpoints
Find all agent clients who have interests in AI
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT uid FROM AgentClient WHERE interests LIKE '%AI%'

NLquery: What are the descriptions of base models created by user with uid 1?
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT description FROM BaseModel WHERE creator_uid = 1

NLquery: Show all LLM services with their domains
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT L.sid FROM LLMService AS L JOIN InternetService AS I ON L.sid = I.sid

NLquery: Count how many customized models exist for each base model
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT bmid FROM CustomizedModel GROUP BY bmid

NLquery: Find the average duration of all model configurations
List all users who are both creators and clients
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT U.uid FROM User AS U JOIN AgentCreator AS AC ON U.uid = AC.uid JOIN AgentClient AS CL ON U.uid = CL.uid

NLquery: What is the most common internet service provider?
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT provider FROM InternetService GROUP BY provider ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC LIMIT 1

NLquery: Show all configurations with duration longer than 100
LLM_returned_SQL_query: SELECT cid FROM ModelConfigurations WHERE duration > 100
